---
description: JankinSunBlog project-wide coding standards
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use TypeScript strict mode; avoid `any`
- Blog posts live in `content/posts/*.md` with frontmatter: title, description, date, tags
- Components in `src/components/` use kebab-case filenames
- Pages in `src/app/` follow Next.js App Router conventions
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling; keep the warm editorial palette (stone/teal on #faf8f5)
- Run `npm run build` after significant changes to verify
- Read `LEARNING.md` for current sprint goals before starting a feature
